work/gaps/G-001-addressed-no-resolver.md:9: error body-prose-id/malformed-shape: G-001 body prose contains id-shaped token "M-foo" that does not match the kind's strict id pattern (wrap in backticks if discussing id syntax) — hint: the body prose contains an id-shaped token that is not a valid id (letter suffix, uppercase placeholder, or narrow-numeric form); fix it with `aiwf edit-body <id>`. If it references a real entity, use the canonical id (`M-0001`, not `M-1` or `M-NNNN`); if it is discussing id syntax, wrap it in backticks. Conversational sequential labels (`M-1`, `M-2`) belong in chat, not committed prose — replace with the allocator-assigned canonical id once the entity exists.
